{
  "scripts": {
    "test": "playwright test",
    "test:ui": "playwright test --ui",
    "test:headed": "playwright test --headed",
    "test:docker": "docker-compose -f docker-compose.test.yml up --build --abort-on-container-exit"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@playwright/test": "^1.40.0",
    "@types/node": "^20.0.0"
  }
}

NOTES:
- Add these scripts to your existing package.json "scripts" section
- Add the devDependencies (merge with existing)
- Adjust versions as needed
- The test:docker script is the recommended way to run tests (no local dependencies needed)
